00:00:29.750 --> 00:00:34.610
It's really great to see you here
tonight for our next installment

00:00:34.610 --> 00:00:36.360
in our exploration
of the collaboration

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:38.950
of the Isamu Noguci
and Martha Graham.

00:00:38.950 --> 00:00:41.380
