00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:22.080
with Noguchi's breath taking
mythic set design for many years.

00:01:22.080 --> 00:01:24.880
Tonight, we hear the curatorial
perspective from someone

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:28.090
who oversees the Noguchi Museum's
exhibitions and collections,

00:01:28.090 --> 00:01:31.090
archives and public programming.

00:01:31.090 --> 00:01:34.220
You'll see a nice line and
Dakin Hart's bio in our program

