that he has the daily good
fortune to collaborate

00:01:36.820 --> 00:01:40.130
with Isamu Noguchi in absentia.

00:01:40.130 --> 00:01:42.490
Before joining the
Noguchi Museum staff,

00:01:42.490 --> 00:01:45.460
Dakin worked as an independent
curator and writer and served

00:01:45.460 --> 00:01:48.480
as an assistant director of
the Nasher Sculpture Center,

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:51.680
