Center for the Arts, and later,

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:56.390
assistant to the director of the
Fine Arts Museums of San Francisco.

00:01:56.390 --> 00:01:58.340
It's been very rewarding
to collaborate

00:01:58.340 --> 00:02:02.550 position:56%
with him specially my colleague Anne
